CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 17, 1970, pg. 6, reads: "Church Leaders Celebrate - The exclusive dining area at the Top of The Towers was the scene of the Pre Christmas Dinner Party given by the Baptist Ministers and their wives recently... Hostesses for the occasion in top left photo are, reading from left, Jackie Walker, Mrs. J. L. Cherry, Mrs. John Walker, chairman; Mrs. Mamie Demps, Miss Gwendolyn Bowick and Mrs. Shirley Langhorn.... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of six women wearing hostess ribbons, left to right: Jackie Walker, Mrs. J. L. Cherry, Mrs. John Walker, Mamie Demps, Gwendolyn Bowick, and Shirley Langhorn, at Baptist Ministers pre-Christmas dinner, Top of the Towers restaurant
